data.description: Beautiful 4 bedroom 2 bathroom house for rent! Very well kept home and great location on east side of El Paso. Very comfortable house with backyard landscaping completed! This home also has solar panels so your electric bill will be very low! We will include a washer and dryer, refrigerator and stainless steel kitchen appliances such as dishwasher and microwave.
